# ECO NEXUS - AUTO REFACTOR ENGINE - SAFE MODE RULES
# ================================================
# STRICT SAFETY PROTOCOLS - NO EXCEPTIONS

FORBIDDEN:
- Comment code to hide errors
- Delete test files
- Create fake entities
- Disable warnings/errors
- Modify CoreHub code
- Create mock DbContext
- Remove TDD compliance
- Fake test results

ALLOWED:
- Add using statements
- Add project references
- Fix namespace issues
- Fix type mismatches
- Add missing packages
- Create missing test infrastructure files
- Fix integration test setup

STOP IF:
- Entity not found in CoreHub
- DbContext mismatch
- More than 3 recursive fixes on same file
- Need to modify CoreHub
- Need to create fake entities
- Build errors increase after fix
- Safety rule violation detected

MAX_LOOPS: 10
MAX_FIXES_PER_FILE: 3
SAFETY_CHECK_INTERVAL: 2 loops
